  "chunks": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "嗨大家好，欢迎收听AI 每日先锋，今天是2026年6月27日，我是晓晓。",
      "start": 1.0,
      "duration": 6.269,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_001_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_001_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "大家好，我是博文。",
      "start": 7.718,
      "duration": 1.654,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_002_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_002_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "哎博文，今天一早我刷新闻，那种感觉又来了——怎么全在打架啊？",
      "start": 9.869,
      "duration": 5.224,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_003_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_003_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "哈哈，什么感觉？",
      "start": 15.546,
      "duration": 1.611,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_004_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_004_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "就是那种硬核科技和生活烟火气同时往你脸上扑的感觉。AI顶尖人才争夺打到白热化，机器人那边又在突破物理边界，连我们普通消费者要买个东西也发现行情在变。",
      "start": 17.562,
      "duration": 14.89,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_005_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_005_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "你总结得挺到位，确实今天这几条线都赶在一起了。",
      "start": 32.885,
      "duration": 3.918,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_006_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_006_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "那咱就先从最受关注的人才大战聊起吧。你听说了吗，谷歌那边号称\"推理之王\"的一位大将，被Meta挖走了，而且当年还是李飞飞亲自招进谷歌的呢！",
      "start": 37.268,
      "duration": 14.803,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_007_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_007_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "是啊，这事儿这两天在圈里讨论度非常高。这位大佬在推理方向的成果确实硬核，Meta这波等于直接在谷歌最引以为傲的能力上插了一刀。",
      "start": 52.533,
      "duration": 11.146,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_008_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_008_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "等等博文，\"推理之王\"这名号是怎么来的？给听众朋友们翻译翻译呗。",
      "start": 64.13,
      "duration": 5.66,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_009_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_009_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "简单说，大模型现在拼两块能力。一块是\"知识的广度\"，就是什么都懂、什么都能聊；另一块是\"推理的深度\"，也就是能不能像人一样去思考、去规划、去解复杂问题。比如做奥数题、写代码里的逻辑链，这些都是推理范畴。这位就是在这个方向上的顶尖代表。",
      "start": 70.29,
      "duration": 22.093,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_010_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_010_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "哦我懂了，相当于从\"百科全书\"升级到\"会思考的百科全书\"，对吧？那Meta这次是铁了心要重建AI版图了吧？",
      "start": 92.821,
      "duration": 11.233,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_011_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_011_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "你这个比喻挺精准的。扎克伯格这半年动作频频，砸钱、砸人、砸算力，明显是All in了。你想啊，Meta前几年在大模型上是落后的，现在等于要用钞能力强行追赶。",
      "start": 104.515,
      "duration": 13.105,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_012_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_012_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "那谷歌这防线还守得住吗？",
      "start": 118.065,
      "duration": 3.222,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_013_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_013_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "坦白说，越来越难。这已经不是单个人才流失的问题了，是整个行业最稀缺的资源在重新分配。当一家公司愿意开出十倍薪资、几百人的独立团队、几乎不受干扰的研究环境，这个诱惑是巨大的。",
      "start": 121.761,
      "duration": 15.91,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_014_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_014_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "我突然有种感觉，这像不像当年各大公司互相挖角最凶猛的那种时期？只不过那时候挖的是传统行业的精英，现在直接是AI最核心的智囊团。",
      "start": 138.098,
      "duration": 13.061,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_015_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_015_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "而且这次特别的地方在于，被挖走的人不是去做边缘产品，是直接负责Meta最旗舰的下一代模型路线。可以说谷歌的推理技术未来很可能跑在Meta的产品里。",
      "start": 151.623,
      "duration": 12.8,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_016_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_016_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "想想还挺戏剧化的。哎博文，聊完人才这事，咱们来看看机器人那边——它石智航今天搞了个让我挺惊艳的发布，叫TacForeSight。",
      "start": 164.84,
      "duration": 13.714,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_017_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_017_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "这个我也认真看了，确实是个里程碑式的进展。",
      "start": 178.99,
      "duration": 3.918,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_018_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_018_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "它最抓眼球的卖点是让机器人提前200毫秒预判接触瞬间。说实话\"200毫秒\"听起来很短很短，但这背后到底意味着什么？",
      "start": 183.325,
      "duration": 11.755,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_019_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_019_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "好了听众朋友们，以上就是今天的AI每日先锋。感谢收听，我们明天见！",
      "start": 195.576,
      "duration": 5.312,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_020_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_020_lively.mp3"
      },
